                                    <p>A double <material>rock</material>-cut <objectType>altar</objectType> with two compartments, one (a) hollowed out to the right, the other shallow (b) to the left  
                                        (dimensions unknown); the hollow of a was closed with a stone lid and contained miniature vases.</p>
                                </support>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
